14 with the confidentiality provisions in subsections (1) and (2) of this section.
15 (7) Additional documents containing information regarding the assets or value of the
16 decedent's estate shall not be ordered to be filed except upon motion with good
17 cause shown, and any document filed under this section shall be in compliance
18 with the confidentiality provisions in subsections (1) and (2) of this section.
